frames.caption: A couple sits at a small round table on a balcony, overlooking a scenic view of a town and distant mountains. The woman, wearing a stylish hat and a coral dress, smiles warmly at the man in a navy suit, who is holding her hand.
frames.description: The scene is set on a charming balcony with a view of a picturesque town and mountains in the background. The couple appears to be enjoying a romantic moment together, surrounded by blooming flowers.

frames.caption: A couple sits on a terrace overlooking a scenic waterfront, engaged in a lively conversation. The woman, dressed in a peach dress and a straw hat, smiles warmly at the man in a navy suit. The background features a serene view of the water and distant mountains under a soft, golden sky.
frames.description: The scene captures a romantic moment between a couple seated on a terrace with a picturesque view of a waterfront and mountains. The setting suggests a leisurely afternoon in a quaint town, with vibrant flowers adding to the charm.
